Package com.amos2020.javabackend.rest_service.request.audit

Provides the classes for requests to create, delete, and update audits. And classes for requests to update the scope of an existing audit project.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateAuditRequest
    Request object for creating a new audit
    DeleteAuditRequest
    Request object for deleting an audit
    UpdateAuditRequest
    Request object for updating an existing audit
    UpdateAuditScopeRequest
    Request object for updating the scope of an existing audit
